  </title>
  <description>
   <narrative xml:lang="EN">A concrete project to start from scratch and bring the communities in the areas hit by the Aug 2016 earthquake back to life again. With your help, over the next few months we intend to fund:  the purchase of a fully-equipped van to sell the produce of local farms hit by the earthquake  the purchase of a mobile dairy fitted out with all the equipment necessary for about 20 farmers  the organization of an Earth Market (Slow Food farmer&apos;s market), purchase of a mobile shop.</narrative>
  </description>
